{"tid":2364949,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"去年狂漲150%！“牛市女皇”的ARK躋身全球十大ETF","createTime":"2021-01-13T11:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T12:33:25.000Z","uid":1086,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69d413cffadf192d8ef766162d6dd874e8c974a3","tid":2364949,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.etf.com/sites/default/files/images/Magazines/ETF%20Report/2018/08/ProfileCatherineWood.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etf.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2FMagazines%2FETF%2520Report%2F2018%2F08%2FProfileCatherineWood.jpg&h=17e53dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨着重倉股特斯拉狂漲7倍，牛市女皇的旗艦產品ARKK淨值也暴漲1.5倍。這吸引了大批資金流入，短短一年時間，ARK資管規模就瘋漲了11倍。<br />\n<br />\n「抱上」特斯拉大腿出圈的Cathie Wood，這下又火了。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社數據顯示，被稱為「牛市女皇」的Cathie Wood旗下的方舟投資管理公司ARK (Ark Investment Management)，<span class=\"red\">在交易所目前總規模5.5萬億美元的ETF中躋身前十，取代了WisdomTree的位置。</span><br />\n<br />\nARK旗下有五項主動型ETF和兩項被動型ETF，目前其管理規模達415億美元，而去年這個時候，ARK的總資產還不到35億美元。<br />\n<br />\nCFRA research的ETF研究主管Todd Rosenbluth表示:「在ETF行業的頭25年裏，對大多數投資者來説，ETF意味著指數產品，而ARK扭轉了這一局面，強調了主動管理可以存在並取得成功。」<br />\n<br />\nCathie Wood又是如何做到的？ARK基金的重倉股特斯拉發揮了重要作用。<br />\n<br />\nARK旗下規模達214億美元的創新電子信託基金ARKK，最大持倉股就是特斯拉。在去年吸引了近100億美元資金後，該基金又迎來了創紀錄的現金認購。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉2020年收益達690.97%，特斯拉股價飆升助推ARKK在2020年實現了150%的漲幅。<br />\n<br />\n當某個創新平台因人們不瞭解而不被看好，ARK卻會加大其權重。<span class=\"red\">在ARK的投資標的中，特斯拉如此，拼多多亦如此。</span><br />\n<br />\n據Cathie Wood，在被動型和指數型投資大行其道的市場，ARK通過&quot;開放研究生態系統&quot;專注於處於成長期的創新企業，相信這些公司將在未來5至10年內帶來長期增長。<br />\n<br />\n對於ARK的勇猛的持倉風格，也有分析人士表示，2020年很大程度上享受了偶發疫情催動的央行流動性盛宴。<br />\n<br />\n投資諮詢公司ETF Store總裁Nate Geraci表示，假設新冠疫苗部署和社會生產恢復正常，經濟將實現復甦，風向將轉向價值型股票，ARK顯然更以增長型為導向，2020年並不具有普適性。"},{"pid":"75a0bbbd26ae5c37602c61f7176dd8e701277c67","tid":2364949,"uid":262183,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0LhH0Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0LhH0Q.png&h=f2acc1e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b7321639390b899597eb89f78212d04a9cb6da2","tid":2364949,"uid":21872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"契媽有渣pdd?"},{"pid":"238394522c804e36837e99fa939333f99e953532","tid":2364949,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b7321639390b899597eb89f78212d04a9cb6da2","tid":2364949,"uid":21872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"契媽有渣pdd?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"ark 5個fund 共買左中資<br />\n騰訊=6.3億USD<br />\nPDD=34M<br />\n百度=7.9億USD<br />\n京東=1.68億USD<br />\n阿里巴巴=1.3億USD<br />\n美團=61.7M<br />\n眾安=41.7M<br />\n移卡=25.9M<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">總共投資左=18.813億USD</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7862f9352018817c6e3a642ce654b53265893d88","tid":2364949,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"契媽有冇買我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d945443b62b97ccefe361f2ecead7a08775dfd7","tid":2364949,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"契媽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7ccb45dbe88440ee9afd2ffd12f9d0a5ebba62","tid":2364949,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"238394522c804e36837e99fa939333f99e953532","tid":2364949,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b7321639390b899597eb89f78212d04a9cb6da2","tid":2364949,"uid":21872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:20:51.000Z","msg":"契媽有渣pdd?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"ark 5個fund 共買左中資<br />\n騰訊=6.3億USD<br />\nPDD=34M<br />\n